{"title":"Deda Alanera RS Reshapes 1st Integrated Handlebar Cockpit to Win Le Tour de France","link":"https://bikerumor.com/deda-alanera-rs-reshapes-1st-integrated-handlebar-cockpit-to-win-le-tour-de-france/","date":1719313200000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_on-a-Standert-bike-1536x1024.jpg\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, on bike\" /></p>\n<p>The carbon Alanera handlebar was one of the first 1-piece integrated cockpits in the pro peloton, and now a lighter Deda Alanera RS has been reshaped to be faster and more comfortable. The changes are subtle but impactful. An all-new aero shape to the tops promises to improve both aerodynamics and rider comfort. And while cables fully disappear inside for modern road compatibility, Deda slightly tweaks the Alanera RS’s ergonomics with a bit of flare and slightly less drop…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Deda Alanera RS 1-piece carbon handlebar cockpit</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, rop\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Deda)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>At first glance, it still looks a lot like the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/eb17-deda-alanera-integrated-superleggera-bars-plus-disc-rim-brake-sl-carbon-wheels/\" target=\"_blank\">original Alanera</a> handlebar + stem combo that we spotted back in 2017. And the same cockpit Tadej <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/deda-auctions-go-tadej-alanera-handlebar-for-pogacar-foundation-cancer-research/\" target=\"_blank\">Pogačar</a> won the Tour on. But there really are several significant improvements, almost hidden in plain sight. The biggest difference comes in the reshaped top – a critical spot where aerodynamics and rider ergonomics meet.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>More aero, more comfy, and lighter too!</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_CFD-aerodynamics.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_CFD-aerodynamics.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, CFD aerodynamics\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_CFD-aerodynamics.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_CFD-aerodynamics-297x186.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_CFD-aerodynamics-1536x960.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_CFD-aerodynamics-120x75.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_CFD-aerodynamics-768x480.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Alanera RS features a 5mm thinner profile for its tops, adopting a truncated aerofoil shape instead of the previous angular quadrilateral. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_new-shape.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_new-shape.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, new aero ergo shape\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_new-shape.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_new-shape-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_new-shape-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_new-shape-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_new-shape-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_new-shape-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Deda says that reshaping alone saves 3.9W at 40 km/h (<em>up to a 15.5W reduction at 60 km/h race speeds</em>)!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_flare.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_flare.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, 6° flare\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_flare.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_flare-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_flare-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_flare-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_flare-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_flare-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides a shape more comfortable to wrap a hand around up top, Deda gives the Alanera RS handlebars 6° of flare to its drops to allow more space for your forearms when you sprint. That flare, plus 10° of UCI allowable shifter inclination means riders can turn those levers in a bit more for an aero hand position. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_comfy-position.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_comfy-position.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, flat top\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_comfy-position.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_comfy-position-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_comfy-position-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_comfy-position-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_comfy-position-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_comfy-position-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Deda redesigned a flatter updated Rapid Hand Movement EVO shape for a smoother transition from your hoods to the tops, with better forearm support. And lastly, bar drop decreases by 10mm to 120mm, sliding them into the more popular compact category.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_monocoque-in-the-mold.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_monocoque-in-the-mold.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, monocoque\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_monocoque-in-the-mold.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_monocoque-in-the-mold-267x300.jpg 267w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_monocoque-in-the-mold-107x120.jpg 107w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_monocoque-in-the-mold-768x864.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All that, and Deda says the updated “full monocoque” one-piece carbon construction with no bonded sections resulted in a smooth internal surface for easy cable routing, a 6% reduction in weight, and best-in-class stiffness-to-weight ratio.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_test-fixture.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"844\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_test-fixture.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, test fixture\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_test-fixture.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_test-fixture-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_test-fixture-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_test-fixture-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_test-fixture-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech specs</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_angled-back.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_angled-back.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, angled\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_angled-back.jpg 600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_angled-back-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_angled-back-120x120.jpg 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_RHM-EVO-side-profile.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_RHM-EVO-side-profile.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, RHM EVO side profile\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_RHM-EVO-side-profile.jpg 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_RHM-EVO-side-profile-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_RHM-EVO-side-profile-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_RHM-EVO-side-profile-768x768.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_angled-with-GPS.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_angled-with-GPS.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, angled with GPS mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_angled-with-GPS.jpg 600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_angled-with-GPS-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_angled-with-GPS-120x120.jpg 120w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Material: full monocoque UD carbon construction</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hardware: black PVD titanium bolts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Curve shape: RHM (<em>Rapid Hand Movement</em>) EVO</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Reach: 75mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Drop: 120 mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Flare: 6° (+2.5cm wider at the ends)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bar widths: 40, 42 &amp; 44cm (<em>measured outside to outside</em>)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Stem angle: -8°</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Stem lengths: 80, 90, 100, 110, 120 &amp; 130mm (<em>140mm on demand</em>)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Steerer size: 1.125″ (<em>28.6mm)</em></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Cable routing: DCR full internal; electronic only for round steerers, or 1x mechanical with a D-shaped steerer</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Clamp height: 43.5 mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Claimed weight: 340g (<em>110×42</em>)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>GPS mount: 36g direct out-front mount for Garmin/Wahoo, Bryton &amp; GoPro, included</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_front-view.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_front-view.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_front-view.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_front-view-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_front-view-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_front-view-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_front-view-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_front-view-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Deda Alanera RS – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-with-GPS-mount.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-with-GPS-mount.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, top with GPS mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-with-GPS-mount.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-with-GPS-mount-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-with-GPS-mount-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-with-GPS-mount-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-with-GPS-mount-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_top-with-GPS-mount-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new 1-piece carbon Deda Alanera RS integrated cockpit is available now for 795€ not including VAT (so figure ~950€ with tax). While that is obviously wildly expensive, it is the same price as the previous model. And it includes the bar, a matching aero top cap, headset spacers, 2 DCR headset covers (for 46 &amp; 56mm headtubes), and the out-front computer mount.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_side-riding.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_side-riding.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Deda Alanera RS 1-piece integrated aero carbon handlebar road bike cockpit, side profile on a bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_side-riding.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_side-riding-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_side-riding-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_side-riding-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_side-riding-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024-Deda-Alanera-RS-1-piece-integrated-aero-carbon-handlebar-road-bike-cockpit_side-riding-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Officially, 13 standard sizes are available with the most popular combination of 6 stem lengths &amp; 3 bar widths. But all size combos are possible on demand, as well as a longer 140mm stem version.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://dedaelementi.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>DedaElementi.com</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/deda-alanera-rs-reshapes-1st-integrated-handlebar-cockpit-to-win-le-tour-de-france/\">Deda Alanera RS Reshapes 1st Integrated Handlebar Cockpit to Win Le Tour de France</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"f944f56b1fcdcefb846c5a3a95831e5c2dbd536071e0598142d8e2da2485d603","category":"Cycling"}